# HttpKernel component

* transform a request into a response
* event driven (via (event) dispatcher and (controller) resolver

# KernelEvents

* REQUEST - perfect for security handling
* CONTROLLER
* VIEW
* RESPONSE
* TERMINATE
* EXCEPTION


